---
title: Hearty Chicken, Potato & Coconut Curry with Brown Rice & Cashews
description: With its gentle warming heat and colourful veggies, a rich and creamy Indian curry is a favourite meal for
good reason! Whip up this veggie version with turnip, broccoli and potato, plus wholesome brown rice that'll
leave you embracing a modern classic.
